---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Dental Practice Marketing in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/medical-dental/dental-practices" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Dental Practices
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Dental Practices</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">10 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Dental Practice Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
          Fill your chair time, reduce no-shows, and build a thriving practice through patient automation.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">
            Dental practice success comes down to filled chairs. Every no-show costs $200-500. Every dormant patient represents lost hygiene revenue. Automation ensures your schedule stays full.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Eliminating No-Shows</h2>

          <p>
            Automated appointment reminders via SMS and email reduce no-shows by 50-70%. Multi-touch sequences (48-hour, same-day, one-hour) give patients multiple opportunities to confirm or reschedule.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Recall Automation</h2>

          <p>
            6-month hygiene recalls shouldn't require staff hours on the phone. Automated recall sequences reach overdue patients systematically, filling hygiene chairs without manual effort.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Treatment Acceptance</h2>

          <p>
            Patients diagnosed with crowns, implants, or cosmetic treatments often never schedule. Automated follow-up converts recommendations into booked procedures and revenue.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-600 to-teal-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Fill Your Schedule?</h3>
            <p class="text-cyan-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd implement these automations for your practice.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-cyan-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
